{"tid":167873,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"發覺其實身邊好多人都有情緒問題","createTime":"2017-03-23T06:51:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-23T08:17:26.000Z","uid":95,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"63bbfbae450a49656bcef46c8ba5f20f7e055418","tid":167873,"uid":95,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T06:51:08.000Z","msg":"唔係講緊一般生活唔如意搞到唔開心嗰啲，係真係有病要食藥嗰種。<br />\n<br />\n我希望大家都可以健健康康開開心心，但呢樣野係無可能的。每個人都有啲心病係無得醫，只可以同呢啲心病一齊生活落去直到死嗰日。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e1e2fd959a5adcb44d7f669d73e5f2becd171be","tid":167873,"uid":86453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T06:53:19.000Z","msg":"係香港咁既地方住 都好難無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4db6adc66acda01e85e9b7482798f7b265f4e943","tid":167873,"uid":95,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T06:58:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係香港咁既地方住 都好難無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢個係殺人社會"},{"pid":"dfaf092361c67418cc35b0eb65b796dbbfc72e92","tid":167873,"uid":51389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T07:10:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>只可以同呢啲心病一齊生活落去直到死嗰日。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9992e7f0c76f4412b937eb0080187a69d3f86a16","tid":167873,"uid":62289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T07:11:26.000Z","msg":"係香港生活 好似要 搵叫錢 讀到書先叫成功 <br />\n 無就係失敗者 好大壓力 <br />\n<br />\n知足常樂呀"},{"pid":"92167f562b0c12fd3c0bbe96657d798a79bfb85a","tid":167873,"uid":69425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T07:13:30.000Z","msg":"記得十年前我睇情緒病嗰陣，醫生話香港每11個人就有1個有，到咗今日，睇怕都應該嚴重咗好多"},{"pid":"56700558a068463070fcb4606249390d32c849a5","tid":167873,"uid":37666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T07:28:14.000Z","msg":"我冇精神問題"},{"pid":"cf85d653f57d942cb33bdb6eb82a022bac1940c8","tid":167873,"uid":95,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T07:56:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>只可以同呢啲心病一齊生活落去直到死嗰日。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係真，過去發生既野你改變唔到，時間亦可能幫唔到你悉懷。all you can do is live with it. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"202abc40b8209c255c022c84fbc85eb9ab46cf29","tid":167873,"uid":95,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T08:00:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係香港生活 好似要 搵叫錢 讀到書先叫成功 <br />\n 無就係失敗者 好大壓力 <br />\n<br />\n知足常樂呀</blockquote><br />\n大學畢業之後入左啲大公司做，眼見啲senior同事日日做到仆街，但人工都唔係多我好多。<br />\n<br />\n係度諗，捱黎都無意思。我只想有份工穩穩定定，每日準時收工番屋企同老婆仔女食飯，放飯一家大細落街食個大快狗早餐，之後晏晝去睇下戲或者一家人去行下山踩下單車就算。"},{"pid":"2909d72c1d77fd856041d02ff7239536daaacd65","tid":167873,"uid":95,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T08:01:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>記得十年前我睇情緒病嗰陣，醫生話香港每11個人就有1個有，到咗今日，睇怕都應該嚴重咗好多</blockquote><br />\n舊時都唔覺身邊的家人朋友有呢啲問題，直到今日先發覺原來連自己都有。"},{"pid":"5778544f8bc92ec41adf2471854cd96184137e09","tid":167873,"uid":51389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T08:16:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我只想有份工穩穩定定，每日準時收工番屋企同老婆仔女食飯，放飯一家大細落街食個大快狗早餐，之後晏晝去睇下戲或者一家人去行下山踩下單車就算。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都只係想有份安穩既工，就算成世冇得升都冇所謂<br />\n可惜永遠都好似俾個天玩咁，次次都係安穩既工做左冇幾耐就要執笠<br />\n<br />\n冇屋企人，冇朋友<br />\n好想死左佢算<br />\n死左就一了百了唔使煩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d3ce5977dba96cbeab22112b106cdbc95db99a6","tid":167873,"uid":95,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T08:17:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我只想有份工穩穩定定，每日準時收工番屋企同老婆仔女食飯，放飯一家大細落街食個大快狗早餐，之後晏晝去睇下戲或者一家人去行下山踩下單車就算。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都只係想有份安穩既工，就算成世冇得升都冇所謂<br />\n可惜永遠都好似俾個天玩咁，次次都係安穩既工做左冇幾耐就要執笠<br />\n<br />\n冇屋企人，冇朋友<br />\n好想死左佢算<br />\n死左就一了百了唔使煩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n試下政府工<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}